What you need to know:

The young coach, who hung his boots three years ago after a successful sojourn in US, had seen a gap in how the careers of Kenyan football players and Africans in general can be shaped to succeed abroadSince the government's ban on sports activities, TTA like most companies has taken the online route, pushing its application, recruitment and training programs onlineKimathi's eight year-stay in the US saw him play at different levels in the academy system including National Collegiate Athletic Association (NCAA) Division 1 level